Revision history for Mojolicious-Plugin-InputValidation

0.10    2020-09-19
        Let pause not index IV_BOOL, NEILB++
0.09    2020-07-09
        Add support for type iv_bool
0.08    2019-01-22
        Allow micro seconds for type iv_datetime
0.07    2018-12-12
        Add additional option 'empty' to accept empty strings
0.06    2018-09-05
        Fix iv_array(of => ...), Horst++
0.05    2018-08-21
        Fix handling of optional elements
0.04    2018-07-28
        Be more backcompat with older perls by removing postderefs
0.03    2018-07-28
        Tell PAUSE to not index private packages
0.02    2018-07-28
        Declare dependency on Mojolicious
0.01    2018-07-27
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

